main event: A witness reported seeing a strange light in the sky from the west that flickered and then moved northwest in Fairborn, Ohio.
interesting points: The sighting was described as part of many occurrences in the Fairborn area., The light flickered but drew no immediate attention., The report was classified as conflicting by Project Blue Book., The witness indicated that there were no photographs included in the report., The questionnaire was filled out as a part of official documentation requests by the US Air Force.
sighted object: a flickering light in the sky
witness description: Witness reported seeing a light with no additional identifying details.
